#TuesdayThoughts  Think about why you are going to #InfoSec / #Hacker conferences. Are you going for the social aspect, or do you actually have a 'I learned a thing' from it? If it is for the social, it's basically a vacation, and that's how your employer might see it too.

The more my personal time becomes limited, the harder the scrutiny I /personally/ put on what I attend and devote volunteer hours to in order to ensure I find value either for personal or career growth. #Conferences

Yes, I personally know the value of social connections. I also want my followers to think about how to not only position the value of conferences but also articulate their take-aways post-conference and how it values the /organization/ that is paying for it.
